    "description": "<strong>WHAT IS MADNESS?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/35c306a2215c40e4418db908c512858a.poster.avif?t=1726076708\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/35c306a2215c40e4418db908c512858a.webm?t=1726076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/35c306a2215c40e4418db908c512858a.mp4?t=1726076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>&quot;Madness Inside&quot; is a psychological horror in the genre of &quot;walking simulator&quot;. In this demo, players can immerse themselves in the atmosphere of the game and go through its first act.<br><br><u><i>Average gameplay demo time:20 min </i></u><br><br>The demo version includes:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Investigation of the initial part of an abandoned psychiatric hospital<br></li><li>A few key puzzles that will help you get to know the mechanics of the game<br></li><li>The first acquaintance with the main character, Lieutenant Vic Voight, and the beginning of his story<br></li><li>An introduction to the dark atmosphere of the game and its elements of horror<br></li><li>Hints and hints on deeper storylines that will be revealed in the full version</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/5e94c63082159d954a438c8ac894eb2e.poster.avif?t=1726076708\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/5e94c63082159d954a438c8ac894eb2e.webm?t=1726076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/5e94c63082159d954a438c8ac894eb2e.mp4?t=1726076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>WARNING: The demo also contains bright lighting effects that can cause seizures in people suffering from photosensitive epilepsy. In addition, there are violent scenes in the game that can negatively affect mental health. Use headphones to fully immerse yourself in the atmosphere of the game.<br><br>Full immersion is recommended using headphones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/4bf87103d74b7104c9a43f8cd73c056e.poster.avif?t=1726076708\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/4bf87103d74b7104c9a43f8cd73c056e.webm?t=1726076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184370/extras/4bf87103d74b7104c9a43f8cd73c056e.mp4?t=1726076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features of the demo version:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Genre: Walking simulator<br></li><li>Built on Unreal Engine 5<br></li><li>Intense atmosphere<br></li><li>Realistic gameplay<br></li><li>Hidden notes and references<br></li><li>Explore an abandoned psychiatric hospital</li></ul>",
